# MF-1: Feature Consistency
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All new features

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Feature Consistency: Maintaining existing functionality unaffected by new features.

ENFORCE: New features must not alter existing functionality; regression tests must confirm.
PROHIBIT: Deploying features that break existing behavior.
ON VIOLATION: Halt deployment → notify orchestrator → log issue.
